	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><em>Haunted: Halloween '85</em> had a problem with jumping from stairs or ramps. It was solved in the sequel by buffering an A press while descending and no more than 8 pixels above the floor. If an A press is buffered, the character jumps the moment he lands.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


